cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper proposes a new optimization algorithm for machine learning problems, specifically for black-box optimization where explicit gradient forms are difficult to obtain. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
